subject: Olympic Games (2010)
Figure Skating
Awards, Decorations and Honors
lead_paragraph: Since finishing third at the 2008 world championships, Kim Yu-na has lost only once, breaking records and raising South Korea’s hopes of its first Olympic gold medal in figure skating.
